                              Share-Your-Ware
                              ===============

Scrotax II is "Share-Your-Ware".  See the Amigaguide for a full explanation
of this.  What this means is that if you play Scrotax II, you should at least
mail me on "semprini@enterprise.net" to tell me how you got on (whether you
like the game or not, if not, I'd like to know why!).

It has taken me 2 years in total to write, so I would appeciate any
feedback, even if it is just "I downloaded Scrotax and it was great!" (I
wish!!).  If you want to slag it off, that's fine, but please say WHY!!

Thank you...

(PS... apologies if you think the above is cheeky!)


